<plot>In addition to showing Colorado's natural wonders, this Traveltalks short visits Buffalo Bill's grave at Lookout Mountain, the Will Rogers memorial at Colorado Springs, and excavations of ancient cliff dwellers at Mesa Verde National Park. The film closes with a choral rendition of "America the Beautiful."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?111076</url></doc>
